com.adidas.ui.activities

Class AdidasWebViewActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • AppCompatActivity
      • com.adidas.ui.activities.AdidasActivity
        • com.adidas.ui.activities.AdidasWebViewActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnTouchListenerRegistrySupport

    public class AdidasWebViewActivity
extends AdidasActivity
    Base activity for WebBased screens. Url to content to load is being extracted from extras of start intent. Has built-in support for content refresh from menu in ActionBar.

      • setForceMobileView

        public void setForceMobileView(boolean mobileView)
        Set if the webview should try to force a phone user agent. This is useful to display a phone layout of a website instead of a desktop layout in a tablet.
        Parameters:
        mobileView - true to force a phone user agent, false to use the the default user agent.
